Feature: 1.7 Uploading photographs
As a Field Engineer
I want to upload the site photographs

Background: 
	Given I have input the installation data required
	And   I have moved to the next page
	Then  I am able to take the photographs
	
	Scenario: Take photographs
		Given I have opened the photograph page
		And   I have selected the photograph name to be taken
		Then  I can use my mobile device to take the photograph

	Scenario: Upload photograph
		Given I have taken the photograph
		And   the photograph is acceptable quality
		And   I click on "upload"
		Then  The photograph is uploaded into the task

	Scenario: Photograph is of un-acceptable quality
		Given I have taken the photograph
		And   the photograph is of un-acceptable quality
		And   I click on the delete icon
		Then  I have deleted the photograph
	